        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">Offers two audit tiers: Snapshot Audit and Advanced Audit. The Snapshot gives a quick read on AI visibility. The Advanced goes deeper with their "6 Pillars" framework. Dashboard-based reporting means you can track changes over time. SaaS pricing model keeps ongoing monitoring affordable. Good option for businesses that want to measure before committing to full optimisation.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Audit covers:</span> Snapshot or Advanced tiers. 6 Pillars framework. Dashboard reporting with ongoing monitoring. From GBP 100/mo for monitoring.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-1">awarenessai.co.uk</p>
      </div>

