          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-text-muted bg-off-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Digital Marketing Agency</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">Uses proprietary Luminr technology to map where a brand appears across traditional and AI search. The audit output shows visibility gaps between traditional search performance and AI search visibility. Works well for larger businesses that need to understand AI search in the context of their broader digital presence. London based.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Audit covers:</span> Luminr-powered visibility mapping. Traditional vs AI search gap analysis. Broader digital context. Enterprise-level reporting.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-1">found.co.uk</p>
