    <div class="mt-16 p-6 bg-off-white rounded-xl border border-border">
      <h2 class="!text-lg mb-3">How to Choose an AI Search Audit</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">Ask three questions. First: how many AI platforms does the audit cover? If the answer is one or two, you are getting an incomplete picture. Second: what signals does the audit measure? "We check if ChatGPT mentions you" is not an audit. Third: does the audit include competitor analysis? Without knowing who AI recommends instead of you, the findings lack context.</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">The best AI search audits also include an ecosystem review - checking your listings, citations, and third-party signals - because AI models do not just look at your website. They look at everything the web says about you.</p>
